<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>When using StaticValue, the value is set using glPointSize(), if available. When using Programmable, gl_PointSize must be set within shader programs, the value provided to this RenderState is ignored in that case.</db:para>
